{"tid":766540,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90後正打靶仔，又話識兩文三語，原來連拼音輸入法都唔識......","createTime":"2018-08-03T16:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T14:44:26.000Z","uid":19334,"like":15,"dislike":138,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"fd629e2cb017df2d4de5c024e048db6727440dbd","tid":766540,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:08:54.000Z","msg":"話說今日幫某公司Interview，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁一開始就有個Skill test，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後先會有Interview，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁間公司就要求考中 / 英文打字 + WORD / EXCEL / POWERPOINT，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為左公平起見，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n考中文試既interviewer就會限定左指定輸入法，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開頭都15 16係用九方定用拼音(我淨係識呢兩隻，同埋語音)，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我發現我打拼音係快過九方(成15 WPM)，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以就決定用左拼音，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知有一批考生(以90後為主)問可唔可以轉其他輸入法，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢話佢唔識打拼音，只係識打倉頡速成，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我話規矩就係規矩，無得改！<br />\n<br />\n之後佢地硬著頭皮咁打(當然係Fail哂，最快好似得40WPM)！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港既兩文三語教育真係失敗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd69d172cf380c5b459c76c6e3eeb274dfaefba5","tid":766540,"uid":15831,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T16:09:11.000Z","msg":"ching ho ball"},{"pid":"c2021606639fa3c97151d690ae111d274d26ece7","tid":766540,"uid":19